Data set:

IMDB

Goal: An anaylsis on Movies through IMDB

Arrange the data in descending order based off the year:

IMDB %>%
  arrange(desc(Year))

Year with most and least releases:

IMDB %>%
  group_by(Year)%>%
  summarize(Total = n())%>%
  
ggplot() +
  geom_col(aes(x=Year, y = Total))

Movies with lowest ratings

IMDB %>%
  na.omit()%>%
  select(Title,Genre,Director,Rating)%>%
  arrange(Rating)%>%
  unique()

Movies with highest ratings

IMDB %>%
  na.omit()%>%
  select(Title,Genre,Director,Rating)%>%
  arrange(desc(Rating))%>%
  unique()
